org.opendaylight.controller.config.api.jmx

Class ObjectNameUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.config.api.jmx.ObjectNameUtil

  • @ThreadSafe
public class ObjectNameUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides ObjectName creation. Each created ObjectName consists of domain that is defined as ON_DOMAIN and at least one key-value pair. The only mandatory property is TYPE_KEY. All transaction related mbeans have TRANSACTION_NAME_KEY property set.
